18:16.660 --> 18:17.705
-I'M GOING ON PATROL.

18:17.835 --> 18:19.054
-SHH! IT'S HIM.

18:19.533 --> 18:20.403
-SONNY?

18:22.013 --> 18:23.145
-SONNY: IT WON'T BE LONG NOW.

18:23.667 --> 18:25.321
