IT ON, DIDN'T YOU?

18:31.110 --> 18:32.241
-OH, I FORGOT.

18:33.460 --> 18:34.287
[SWITCH CLICKS]

18:35.201 --> 18:36.724
[SCRAMBLING NOISE]

18:36.854 --> 18:37.638
-DAMN IT!

18:37.768 --> 18:39.074
-WHAT?

18:39.205 --> 18:40.510
-SHE PUT A SCRAMBLER
