18:40.641 --> 18:42.033
-WHEN I WAS IN THE
NAVY SEALS, WE USE TO--

18:42.164 --> 18:45.036
-HEY. I WON'T PRETEND I
CAN DO YOUR JOB ANYMORE

18:45.167 --> 18:46.908
