19:41.658 --> 19:44.922
-I TRIED. I SAVED HER
LIFE AND SHE WON'T GO.

19:45.053 --> 19:46.924
-WELL, THIS BOAT ISN'T BIG
ENOUGH FOR THE BOTH OF US.

19:47.055 --> 19:48.752
