19:48.883 --> 19:52.234
-COME ON, C.J. THERE'S
GOTTA BE A WAY.

19:53.627 --> 19:56.456
-WELL, YEAH. SHE CAN SAVE
YOUR LIFE AND YOU'D BE EVEN.

19:56.586 --> 19:57.892
