26:07.827 --> 26:09.568
-WE STILL DO.

26:09.698 --> 26:12.266
WE'RE NOT DOIN' LUNCH. WE'RE
NOT HAVING COCKTAILS AT SUNSET.

26:12.962 --> 26:15.312
-YOU AGREED TO STAY
OUT OF FBI BUSINESS.

26:15.443 --> 26:17.532
BECAUSE OF YOUR PHONE CALL,
I COULDN'T PLANT THIS BUG.

26:17.663 --> 26:18.968
YOU COULD VERY WELL
HAVE JEOPARDIZED

26:19.099 --> 26:20.535
A LENGTHY BUREAU SURVEILLANCE.

26:20.666 --> 26:21.536
-REALLY?

26:22.406 --> 26:23.843
I THOUGHT I SAVE THE WHOLE DEAL,

26:23.973 --> 26:25.409
NOT TO MENTION
YOUR PERSONAL BUTT,

26:25.540 --> 26:27.498
NOT TO MENTION YOUR
ENTIRE LIFE OUT THERE.

26:28.935 --> 26:30.719
-SOUNDS LIKE YOU WANT
A MEDAL OR SOMETHING.

26:30.850 --> 26:33.504
-NO, BUT A SIMPLE
THANK YOU WOULD SUFFICE.

26:35.506 --> 26:37.857
-THANK YOU. YOU SAVED MY LIFE.

26:37.987 --> 26:39.815
YOU'RE MY HERO. FEEL BETTER?

26:39.946 --> 26:41.774
-OH, YOU HAD ME PEGGED
AS A DUMB WAVE JOCKEY

26:41.904 --> 26:42.862
BEFORE YOU EVEN MET ME.

26:43.514 --> 26:45.125
AND YOU WERE WRONG THEN
AND YOU'RE WRONG NOW.

26:45.255 --> 26:46.909
ONLY PROBLEM IS YOU
HAVEN'T GOT THE GUTS

26:47.040 --> 26:48.955
TO ADMIT YOU'RE WRONG, HAVE YOU?

26:50.043 --> 26:51.044
[PHONE RINGS]

26:51.174 --> 26:52.349
-BUCHANNON.

26:55.178 --> 26:56.310
IT'S FOR YOU.

26:59.879 --> 27:01.010
-THIS IS CHRISTOPHER.

27:03.447 --> 27:04.535
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

27:05.798 --> 27:07.190
I HAVE TO GO TO HEADQUARTERS.

27:08.191 --> 27:10.193
-KEYS ARE IN MY TRUCK.

27:12.021 --> 27:14.241
TRY NOT TO RUN OVER ANYBODY!

27:22.162 --> 27:23.816
[TRUCK ENGINE CRANKS]

27:25.339 --> 27:26.819
-THIS IS BUCHANNON.

27:26.949 --> 27:28.429
I'M GONNA BE OUT OF MY
TOWER FOR A LITTLE WHILE.

27:28.559 --> 27:31.040
HAVE SOMEBODY WATCH
MY WATER. THANK YOU.

27:31.171 --> 27:34.740
[MYSTERIOUS MUSIC]

27:44.793 --> 27:46.055
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

27:47.927 --> 27:48.841
-COMING.

27:52.409 --> 27:54.498
-HI. REMEMBER ME?

27:55.108 --> 27:56.587
-THE JELLYFISH MAN.

27:56.718 --> 27:58.589
-RIGHT. OH, YOU DIDN'T
STEP ON ANY, DID YOU?

27:58.720 --> 28:01.288
-NO. LOOK, I'M REALLY
KINDA BUSY RIGHT NOW.

28:01.418 --> 28:03.377
-WELL, THIS WON'T
TAKE A SECOND.

28:03.507 --> 28:05.509
I'M GOING DOOR TO DOOR TO TRY
AND GET PEOPLE TO SPONSOR ME

28:05.640 --> 28:07.120
FOR THE LIFEGUARD OLYMPICS.

28:07.250 --> 28:09.949
IT'S FOR CHARITY. REALLY,
WHATEVER YOU CAN GIVE.

28:10.079 --> 28:11.559
-SORRY.

28:11.690 --> 28:13.387
-ALL THE MONEY GOES TO
UNDERPRIVILEGED CHILDREN.

28:13.517 --> 28:14.867
IT'S A TAX WRITE-OFF.

28:15.476 --> 28:16.564
PLEASE?

28:17.434 --> 28:18.522
FOR THE CHILDREN.

28:20.133 --> 28:21.569
-I'LL GET MY PURSE.
IT'S UPSTAIRS.

28:21.700 --> 28:22.613
-THANK YOU.

28:27.401 --> 28:30.970
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

28:44.418 --> 28:45.288
[DOOR CLOSES]

28:48.465 --> 28:51.468
GREAT VIEW. I CAN ACTUALLY
SEE MY TOWER FROM HERE.

28:52.556 --> 28:55.690
[PEOPLE TALKING
INDISTINCTLY IN BACKGROUND]

29:01.304 --> 29:03.306
-TANYA: OKAY, SO WHO
DO I WRITE THIS OUT TO?

29:03.437 --> 29:05.091
-MITCH: BAYWATCH LIFEGUARDS.

29:06.266 --> 29:07.571
IT'S REALLY TERRIFIC OF YOU

29:07.702 --> 29:09.008
TO SUPPORT THE
LIFEGUARD ASSOCIATION.

29:09.138 --> 29:10.879
IT'LL MAKE
A LOT OF CHILDREN HAPPY.

29:11.010 --> 29:12.925
YOU'RE A GOOD NEIGHBOR
AND A GREAT SWIMMER.

29:13.969 --> 29:16.406
-THANK YOU. OKAY,
HOW WILL THIS DO?

29:16.537 --> 29:17.843
-OH, THAT'S TERRIFIC.

29:17.973 --> 29:19.758
WELL, THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

29:19.888 --> 29:21.934
-UH, ACTUALLY, YOU CAN GO
OUT THIS WAY IF YOU'D LIKE.

29:22.717 --> 29:23.631
-THANK YOU.

29:26.765 --> 29:30.638
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

29:42.563 --> 29:46.654
[BIRDS SQUAWKING]

30:01.974 --> 30:05.934
[COUGHS]

