31:52.388 --> 31:53.912
-YOU REALLY SAVED HIS LIFE?

31:55.087 --> 31:56.175
-I JUST TRIED TO HELP.

31:56.784 --> 31:58.177
-SHE REALLY SAVED YOUR LIFE!

31:58.307 --> 31:59.308
-HUH?

31:59.830 --> 32:01.615
-TELL HER
HOW GRATEFUL YOU ARE.

32:01.745 --> 32:03.269
-YEAH, YEAH, RIGHT.

32:03.399 --> 32:07.969
GRETA, YOU OWED ME YOUR
LIFE, NOW I OWE YOU MINE.

32:08.883 --> 32:11.277
TO THE RESPECT OF YOUR
GRANDFATHER'S GRANDFATHER,

32:12.669 --> 32:15.934
AND TO THE WAY, WE'RE EVEN.

32:17.718 --> 32:18.893
[GRETA GIGGLES]

32:19.024 --> 32:19.894
-OW!

32:31.906 --> 32:33.473
-OKAY, I ADMIT IT.

32:34.909 --> 32:36.737
I MIGHT HAVE A BIT
OF AN ATTITUDE.

32:40.349 --> 32:42.482
-A BIT? MIGHT?

32:44.701 --> 32:48.444
-THERE WAS SOMEONE, A SURFER.

32:51.186 --> 32:53.536
ALWAYS CHASING
AFTER THE NEXT WAVE,

32:53.667 --> 32:55.538
THE NEXT PRETTY GIRL.

32:56.148 --> 32:58.150
HE PROMISED ME HE'D
ALWAYS BE THERE FOR ME.

33:01.283 --> 33:04.025
HE LEFT. HE NEVER CAME BACK.

33:05.374 --> 33:06.767
-WHAT, AN OLD BOYFRIEND?

33:08.334 --> 33:09.378
-MY FATHER.

33:11.293 --> 33:13.078
HE BROKE MY HEART
AND MY MOTHER'S.

33:15.036 --> 33:18.083
SO, YOU SEE, I'M NOT TOO
FOND OF THE BEACH BOYS.

33:21.042 --> 33:23.653
-OKAY. I HEAR YA.

33:25.742 --> 33:28.919
-THANK YOU. FOR EVERYTHING.

33:30.834 --> 33:32.880
-DOES THIS MEAN WE CAN
HAVE COCKTAILS AT SUNSET?

33:34.838 --> 33:35.926
-PROBABLY.

33:42.933 --> 33:44.892
5 O'CLOCK, RIGHT ON TIME.

33:54.554 --> 33:56.556
-WHAT MADE YOU
BECOME AN FBI AGENT?

33:59.385 --> 34:01.343
-WHEN I WAS LITTLE,
WE WENT ON A TOUR

34:01.474 --> 34:03.389
