IN WASHINGTON.

34:05.347 --> 34:08.045
AND FROM THEN ON, I KNEW IT'S
WHAT I ALWAYS WANTED TO DO.

34:11.353 --> 34:13.399
WHAT MADE YOU DECIDE
TO BE A LIFEGUARD?

34:14.226 --> 34:16.750
-WHEN I WAS LITTLE,
WE CAME TO THE BEACH.

34:18.578 --> 34:20.232
-I GUESS WE BOTH
MADE CAREER CHOICES

34:20.362 --> 34:21.972
AT PRETTY EARLY AGE, HUH?

34:22.495 --> 34:23.364
-YEAH.

34:24.409 --> 34:26.889
[PEOPLE TALKING
INDISTINCTLY IN BACKGROUND]

34:30.110 --> 34:30.981
-WHAT?

34:32.373 --> 34:34.550
-TANYA. SHE'S IN TROUBLE.

34:36.726 --> 34:39.554
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

34:40.382 --> 34:42.558
[WAVES CRASH]

34:50.871 --> 34:52.960
-BAYWATCH, THIS IS
FBI AGENT CHRISTOPHER,

34:53.091 --> 34:54.440
WE HAVE AN EMERGENCY
SITUATION HERE.

34:54.570 --> 34:56.311
WE NEED BACKUP.
SEND A [INDISTINCT].

