35:28.038 --> 35:30.345
[WAVES CRASH]

35:35.655 --> 35:38.048
-DEWEY! DOWN HERE!

35:39.180 --> 35:42.140
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

35:52.106 --> 35:53.890
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

35:55.370 --> 35:56.415
-WE CAN'T FIND HER!

35:56.545 --> 35:57.416
-MITCH!

35:58.765 --> 36:00.636
-SHE KNOCKED THE WATER
OUT OF HER LEFT EAR.

36:00.767 --> 36:02.072
SHE FAKED THE DROWNING.

36:02.203 --> 36:03.117
THAT'S TANYA AND
SONNY ON THAT BOAT.

36:03.248 --> 36:04.640
ALL RIGHT, DEWEY, LET'S GO.

36:04.771 --> 36:06.164
-NO, I'M COMING WITH YOU.

36:06.294 --> 36:07.165
-IT'S OKAY.

36:09.123 --> 36:10.994
[BOAT MOTOR HUMS]

36:11.778 --> 36:13.301
[ENGINE REVS]

36:19.873 --> 36:21.266
-ALL RIGHT, TAKE THE CONTROLS.

36:21.396 --> 36:23.398
-YOU TAKE THE CONTROLS.
JUST GET ME CLOSER.

36:23.529 --> 36:24.617
-I KNOW WHAT I'M DOING HERE.

36:24.747 --> 36:26.401
-SO DO I. JUST GET ME CLOSER.

36:27.576 --> 36:28.708
COME ON!

36:31.014 --> 36:34.496
[INTENSE MUSIC]

36:35.889 --> 36:37.673
[ENGINE REVS]

36:54.647 --> 36:56.257
[GRUNTS]

37:05.397 --> 37:06.267
-AH!

37:09.444 --> 37:11.490
[SONNY GRUNTS]

37:19.062 --> 37:19.933
-AH!

37:25.243 --> 37:26.679
[MITCH GROANS]

37:30.639 --> 37:33.033
[SONNY GRUNTS IN PAIN]

37:36.471 --> 37:40.736
[INTENSE MUSIC]

38:01.627 --> 38:02.715
-TO US.

38:02.845 --> 38:03.716
-TO US.

38:07.110 --> 38:09.069
YOU KNOW, IF YOU HADN'T
BEEN SO OBSERVANT,

38:09.199 --> 38:11.158
