GOTTEN AWAY WITH IT.

38:12.246 --> 38:13.334
-WHAT'D YOU SAY? [CHUCKLES]

38:14.640 --> 38:16.337
-DON'T BE ARROGANT,
MITCH BUCHANNON.

38:16.468 --> 38:17.991
